tpb (0.6.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * new upstream version
  * use gettext for the debconf templates (Closes: #202201)
  * french translation for debconf templates, thanks to Michel Grentzinger
    <mic.grentz@online.fr> (Closes: #202202)
